snippet.title: Persona 3: Dancing in Moonlight - SEES Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet the Specialized Extracurricular Extermination Squad (SEES) and get a first look at some of their Social scenes and English voiceover from Persona 3: Dancing in Moonlight!

Persona 3: Dancing in Moonlight and Persona 5: Dancing in Starlight launch on PlayStation®4 and PlayStation®Vita on December 4, 2018!

Get more info and pre-order now at http://atlus.com/personadancing.
